                <p
                    style="font-size: 0.8rem; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(196,181,253,0.8); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.14em; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
                    ‚ú¶ Get Started Today ‚ú¶
                </p>
                <h2
                    style="font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.25rem); font-weight: 800; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">
