                    <span style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);">is one session away.</span>
                </h2>
                <p
                    style="font-size: 1rem; color: rgba(203,213,225,0.75); margin-bottom: 2.5rem; line-height: 1.8; max-width: 520px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">
                    Join thousands of professionals leveling up their skills with expert-led 1:1 sessions.
                </p>
                <div class="cta-btn-container">
                    <a href="/signup" class="cta-btn-primary">Book a Session</a>
                    <a href="/signup" class="cta-btn-secondary">Become a Host ‚Üí</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

